title: Democratic Congressman John Garamendi
itunes:title: Democratic Congressman John Garamendi
description:
Kevin spoke with Amos Snead, Executive Vice President of ADFERO and Co-founder of FamousDC, and Luis Miranda, Former DNC Communications Director. They discussed the whistle-blower complaint and comments from acting intelligence chief, Joseph Maguire.

Kevin also spoke with Democratic Congressman John Garamendi of California.
